        <Parent_String>Native American wearing blankets [300244290], wearing blankets by origin or style [300244287], wearing blankets [300197421], outerwear [300209265], clothing [300266639], costume (mode of fashion) [300178802], Costume (hierarchy name) [300209261], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
